  <brief_title>Cranberry Juice in the Prevention of Urinary Tract Infections in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy of Cranberry Juice in the Prevention of Urinary Tract Infections in Children - Randomized, Placebo Controlled Multi-Center Study</official_title>
